# build / editable install artifacts
*.egg-info/
dist/
build/
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# pilot outputs — committed so findings are readable from the repo,
# regenerable with the scripts for anyone with the model cached.

# hidden-state sidecars — ~50 MB per generation × ~1500 generations
# = way too big for git. Regenerable from the pilot/emotional runners
# with the model cached. Local-only by design.
data/local/hidden/

# local envs
.venv/
.env

# run logs — ad-hoc tee'd output, not part of the experimental record
logs/

# editor cruft
.DS_Store
.idea/
.vscode/
.claude/

# Snapshot of the contributor-submitted HF dataset
# (a9lim/llmoji); regenerable via scripts/harness/06_claude_hf_pull.py.
data/harness/hf_dataset/

# Multi-layer h_mean tensors for the v3 follow-on analyses
# (scripts 21, 23). ~800 MB per model (npz compression doesn't help
# with dense float32 hidden states); one-shot rebuild from the
# data/local/hidden/<experiment>/*.npz sidecars via the loader's
# cache_path arg.
data/local/cache/

# Per-script ad-hoc outputs that aren't part of the experimental record:
data/local/phase_timing_smoke/

# Working backups of JSONLs from the seed-0 cache-mode-mismatch
# fix (2026-05-03). Kept locally during the fix verification, not
# part of the experimental record.
data/**/*.bak.*

# === Privacy-sensitive outputs (post-2026-05-06) ===========================
# Outputs derived from a contributor's local emission journal +
# claude.ai exports + named-project breakdown. Kept regenerable via
# the scripts (66_per_project_quadrants, 67_wild_residual,
# 68_three_way_analysis with --include-local) but never committed —
# the rendered tables, figures, and per-(face, surface) joins reveal
# deployment telemetry that doesn't belong in a public repo.
data/harness/empathic_concern_user_text_*.{md,tsv,jsonl}
data/harness/claude_per_project_*.{md,tsv}
data/harness/wild_faces_labeled*.tsv
figures/harness/claude_per_project_*.png
figures/harness/wild_faces_pca_3d*.html
# Auto-regenerated cluster docs that bake in deployment-surface
# categories from local data. Regen locally with script 67.
docs/2026-MM-DD-residual-state-axes*.md
docs/2026-??-??-residual-state-axes*.md
